1. *Park* je lep u svim godišnjim dobima. (The park is beautiful in all seasons.)
2. *Park* je pun ljudi u letnjim mesecima. (The park is full of people in the summer months.)
3. Spustio sam se do *parka*. (I went down to the park.)
4. Moja kuća je u blizini *parka*. (My house is close to the park.)
5. Ona šeta svaku veče u *parku*. (She takes a walk every night in the park.)
6. Oni se igraju u *parku*. (They are playing in the park.)
7. Oni su šetali *parkom*. (They were walking through the park.)
8. Ona se igrala sa svojim prijateljima u *parku*. (She was playing with her friends in the park.)